<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <title>New Reality Question</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        .container {
            width: 80%;
            margin: auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .header {
            background-color: #f2f2f2;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .content {
            margin: 20px 0;
            padding: 20px;
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
            border-radius: 10px;
        }
        .footer {
            margin-top: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 0.9em;
            color: #555;
        }
        .code {
            font-family: "Courier New", Courier, monospace;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            padding: 1px;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }
        p.links {
            display: flex; 
            justify-content: space-evenly;
            gap: 20px; 
            width: 100%;
        }
        img {
            vertical-align: middle; 
            margin-right: 5px;
            width: 24px;
        }
        h3 {
            margin-block-start: 1em;
            margin-block-end: -0.5em;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>ðŸ—³ New Reality Question!</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <p>Hey there,</p>
            <p>A new Reality question has been created for a Snapshot proposal in the space <b><%- notification.space.ens %></b>.</p>
            <p class="links">
                <a href="<%- getRealityQuestionLink(notification) %>"><img src="../assets/reality.png" alt="Reality" />Reality Question</a>
                <a href="<%- getSnapshotProposalLink(notification) %>"><img src="../assets/snapshot.png" alt="Snapshot" />Snapshot Proposal</a>
                <a href="https://etherscan.io/tx/<%- notification.event.txHash %>"><img src="../assets/etherscan.png" alt="Etherscan" />Transaction</a>
            </p>
            <h3>Details</h3>
            <p>
                Reality Question ID: <span class="code"><%- notification.event.questionId %></span><br/>
                Snapshot Proposal ID: <span class="code"><%- notification.event.proposalId %></span><br/>
            </p>

        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>Best regards,<br>Kleros Zodiac Notifications Bot</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>